      "heading": "Versatile 4 MP Bullet Camera",
      "text": "UniFi Video Camera G4 Bullet is an all-weather IP camera designed for surveillance in all conditions, made of highly durable materials cast aluminum and weatherproof ABS plastic. The design is made in accordance with the high standards of cameras for outdoor video surveillance. There is no need for additional protection during installation. The housing is very sturdy and at the same time very compact. Therefore, many people use this model for indoor video surveillance."
